title: Python UDFs in SQL. Who is using?
text:
Who is using Python UDFs in SQL?

Lately I've seen many of the data-warehouses/lakes providers rolling out features that let's you run Python UDFs as part of your SQL command. And, runs it close to the data.

Show HN: MightyShare – Automatically generate social share images in WordPress
text:
Hey HN!

Looking for feedback on my new WordPress plugin. The plugin takes your WordPress title/featured image to create a social share image. If you want to try it out a free account is required and is easy to add to your WordPress site.

If you have any questions just let me know.
